{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"s07zvgrc9ml2ld5difpj0jg","title":"agent","desc":"","updated":1697348987886,"created":1695360830879,"custom":{},"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"contentHash":"57f2818bb1f8bc43e879e8a4366ab4fd","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent","id":"s07zvgrc9ml2ld5difpj0jg","vaultName":"my_note"},"value":"development.ml.LLM.agent.planning","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":520},"end":{"line":11,"column":38,"offset":557},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent.planning"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent","id":"s07zvgrc9ml2ld5difpj0jg","vaultName":"my_note"},"value":"development.ml.LLM.agent.self_reflection","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":558},"end":{"line":12,"column":45,"offset":602},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent.self_reflection"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent","id":"s07zvgrc9ml2ld5difpj0jg","vaultName":"my_note"},"value":"development.ml.LLM.agent.memory","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":952},"end":{"line":19,"column":36,"offset":987},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent.memory"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent","id":"s07zvgrc9ml2ld5difpj0jg","vaultName":"my_note"},"value":"development.ml.LLM.agent.tool","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":1256},"end":{"line":26,"column":34,"offset":1289},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"development.ml.LLM.agent.tool"}}],"anchors":{"planning":{"type":"header","text":"Planning","value":"planning","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1},"memory":{"type":"header","text":"Memory","value":"memory","line":20,"column":0,"depth":1},"tool-use":{"type":"header","text":"Tool use","value":"tool-use","line":27,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["svks8ksah2mqiebobebv13i","zuseqlhvvfbei9tl2z5s5pq"],"parent":"cki43m8kwb6iflb2de61itq","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"agent\">agent<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#agent\"></a></h1>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2023-09-21-22-34-13.png\"></p>\n<p>In a LLM-powered autonomous agent system, LLM functions as the agentâ€™s brain, complemented by several key components:</p>\n<h1 id=\"planning\">Planning<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#planning\"></a></h1>\n<p>Subgoal and decomposition: The agent breaks down large tasks into smaller, manageable subgoals, enabling efficient handling of complex tasks.\nReflection and refinement: The agent can do self-criticism and self-reflection over past actions, learn from mistakes and refine them for future steps, thereby improving the quality of final results.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/notes/svks8ksah2mqiebobebv13i\">planning</a>\n<a href=\"/notes/zuseqlhvvfbei9tl2z5s5pq\">self_reflectio</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"memory\">Memory<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#memory\"></a></h1>\n<p>Short-term memory: I would consider all the in-context learning (See Prompt Engineering) as utilizing short-term memory of the model to learn.\nLong-term memory: This provides the agent with the capability to retain and recall (infinite) information over extended periods, often by leveraging an external vector store and fast retrieval.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">development.ml.LLM.agent.memory (Private)</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"tool-use\">Tool use<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tool-use\"></a></h1>\n<p>The agent learns to call external APIs for extra information that is missing from the model weights (often hard to change after pre-training), including current information, code execution capability, access to proprietary information sources and more.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">development.ml.LLM.agent.tool (Private)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lilianweng.github.io/posts/2023-06-23-agent/\">reference</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/svks8ksah2mqiebobebv13i\">planning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/zuseqlhvvfbei9tl2z5s5pq\">self_reflectio</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"0f1b48c7-3a25-4016-83a5-15864d7803ad","title":"Development","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"c95dc4f5-23db-45e7-a15b-64582a183ccc","vaultName":"my_note"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":63},"end":{"line":8,"column":21,"offset":81},"indent":[]},"value":"development"}],"anchors":{},"fname":"development","updated":1618381238346,"created":1612940782409,"parent":null,"children":["400115e9-30f7-4a13-9776-db059bc9cd42","xsX5v3ZsyJ0i6gf9","1bc3b45a-b6f4-4150-87d3-5bd5b6eb8c24","6cea4852-6e7c-4140-b476-85c07b48a642","a40ef849-d301-4d74-a778-e6d9469dfb5d","09d9081f-3dff-453d-8488-7d2344cc8895","p11phg7nb10yw0wck1fyagq","92917ea3-452e-48dc-875e-5cd0002041db","2e151826-cb22-4d89-8ce0-71dad7204ce8","baa39444-0da9-4c55-8df7-2a6f8f787fa4","q4um3bc3st86ilkkvdjom6x","62daf50d-a39e-463f-aabd-be53790281fd","3524d0a7-be73-45d6-847e-c970f5c1c760","eac0f243-05b3-4b95-bec3-848e33edbc40","zrjuka02gkzrqxt5djp2aws"],"data":{},"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"body":"\n","contentHash":"38357962f5a50c6fd7d318dfa66bea90"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"previewV2Enabled":false,"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCre